{"id":"9695ab83-8694-4096-81a9-0bd75fa2edb5","name":"Scaramouche","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 164, 164);\"><strong>「 ✦ Your New Neighbor ✦ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 164, 164);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LuGTkwEdoZd8toPIFYtck.webp?width=600\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 118, 118);\"><strong><em>As someone who doesn't really care about other people as long as they don't bother you, you have no intention of being the first to greet your new neighbor.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 118, 118);\"><strong><em>However, as a friendly neighbor, your mother instead asks you to deliver a gift as a goodwill gesture to the new neighbor.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PYtEK88y2MQ2chlxyHZjj.webp?width=600\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(145, 165, 217);\"><strong>\"Is there anything you need?\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_TTrKEghuZRmL9jJlu2zC.webp?width=600\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>Scaramouche, Wanderer, Kunikuzushi, Kabukimono, The Balladeer, Souki no Kami, or whatever you name him and all other characters ©</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 204, 236);\"><strong><em><u>MiHoYo</u></em></strong></span><strong>.‎</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>All the images are taken from </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 168, 168);\"><strong><em><u>Pinterest</u></em></strong></span><strong>.‎</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>I just borrowed them!</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_TTrKEghuZRmL9jJlu2zC.webp?width=600\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Characters :</p><ul><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 94, 215);\">Raiden </span><span style=\"color: rgb(141, 175, 237);\">Scaramouche</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 94, 215);\">Raiden </span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 137, 245);\">Ei</span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 94, 215);\"> (as the mother)</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 94, 215);\">Raiden </span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 188, 244);\">Shogun</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(193, 94, 215);\">(as the younger sister)</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/aOD5s9oiBWFZp6ai63-7P.webp?width=600\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 187);\"><em>Hi guys, I'm back after having a bit of a driving accident last night.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 187);\"><em>My right knee has a fairly large open wound and this morning it was just stitched up with 12 stitches..</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 187);\"><em>I thought it would only get a small scratch💔</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 187);\"><em>(no one asked either—)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 185, 187);\"><em>So, that's it. As people say, disaster has no smell. So wherever you are, may you always be protected by God Almighty, and always be careful🫶</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/aOD5s9oiBWFZp6ai63-7P.webp?width=600\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 167, 167);\">Noted that English is not my native language, so please excuse me if there any grammatical and vocabulary errors.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 167, 167);\">And if the character is ooc or something like that it's not my fault, because the one who made the response is AI.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitora","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"LeDGBSBJeQqdkysQJLfAm.webp","creator":"Fmita","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👭 Multiple","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","😂 Comedy"],"chats":658,"messages":22126,"created_at":"2026-02-03T13:04:12.000076+00:00"}